title: Psychowave - Sunshine Reborn
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Drawing influence and inspiration from old school psytrance and Goa trance music, Psychowave tries to merge deep vintage atmospheres from the past with new sound design possibilities. Neogoa now delivers fresh Brazilian psychedelia with Sunshine Reborn, an acid-driven Goa trance release which will make you dance under the warm rays of sun. Download Sunshine Reborn - http://www.neogoa.net/sunshine-reborn

Tracklist:

01 - Supernova (145 BPM) 
02 - Sunshine Reborn (145 BPM) 
03 - Tranceship To The Sun (144 BPM) 
04 - Dancem Macacos, Dancem (146 BPM) 
05 - Innertrip (144 BPM)

For more free Goa trance and ambient music, please visit us:
